{"tid":186123,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇 IT 人想創業?","createTime":"2017-04-04T03:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T12:09:43.000Z","uid":102981,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7609759c675d75562b812becd518de5c2a40649b","tid":186123,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"我開左個 TG group，希望有班有心創業既IT人可以大家互補<br />\n<br />\n除左個講字，真係要有技術落手落腳整。<br />\n<br />\n先唔講最後有冇成果。<br />\n<br />\n如果你可以利用工餘時間，或者自己已經試緊創業，可以入 group，睇下有冇人可以一齊參與。<br />\n<br />\n個 group 係為想離開打工仔生涯既IT人而設，並唔係搵工。屬於做實事多過吹水。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAECH7qDtLNkrtlBOvQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAECH7qDtLNkrtlBOvQ&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4bd65aab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAECH7qDtLNkrtlBOvQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個討厭被叫 IT 狗既 IT 人  字"},{"pid":"195c73b24333e3c3187c047b920215bf604fd022","tid":186123,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"linux ?"},{"pid":"f5e87e716b03f5fc76d25d3a32ae95520ce2f869","tid":186123,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"同叫人見工比完意見點樣改善公司就話唔請有咩分別???"},{"pid":"9d78124497e08a00a3e571f5b0dbe1077c86636a","tid":186123,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"點解呢行會俾人當狗, 就係有你呢D想要成果又唔肯比錢用所謂創業黎昆鳩人既仆街老細. 人工比唔起就算, 而家想免費拎橋, 食屎啦"},{"pid":"1541b591000ff707e2e8e5ee2b0ffbc67619a4b8","tid":186123,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解呢行會俾人當狗, 就係有你呢D想要成果又唔肯比錢用所謂創業黎昆鳩人既仆街老細. 人工比唔起就算, 而家想免費拎橋, 食屎啦</blockquote><br />\n我做到老細就唔駛打工啦<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得條橋係唔講得俾人知, 可以收埋<br />\n簡單既橋，例如做個討論區，lihkg 都做得起。<br />\n好多野都係差個人去做"},{"pid":"8799202c3139c6203e4612a9a4b5b8a99f6a7bc1","tid":186123,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:25:29.000Z","msg":"IT 狗"},{"pid":"7e2cce7286aeee03b75f67d74054287e3de09c41","tid":186123,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:55:06.000Z","msg":"可能又係嗰啲你出idea, IT狗出技術嘅世紀大騙局? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9468a0d2d81810b92bd4edd44bfb8f9cd452d740","tid":186123,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"我有個idea, 但唔識寫program ⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"d86c8a1f83055e20d14a8b81d3f3ccd007b53c34","tid":186123,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能又係嗰啲你出idea, IT狗出技術嘅世紀大騙局? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n擺明係，香港好撚多呢d 仆街"},{"pid":"7e31d75ab38abd696ba0ecd72d0be304c2925e5e","tid":186123,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"去d創業活動同d BBA佬夾，個個都係吹水王<br />\n即使個idea係你出又點<br />\n擺明你識寫code你永遠只配做佢手下<br />\n一幅高高在上的樣子"},{"pid":"2561041312b7db3e7e30639ce299757c24dffc19","tid":186123,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:55:55.000Z","msg":"暫時都係識寫 program 既人入 group 多"},{"pid":"394f41e0e00e32f3d08767a51c3a21574cefe372","tid":186123,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"年年都有呢d 狗屎垃圾谷呃IT狗入去創業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b41c76ab8d473ad525b1f86b22a2b166cf7b4b","tid":186123,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:21:58.000Z","msg":"呢個世界好多時都係嗰啲識得呃呃騙騙嘅人先會發達, 反而做實事嘅人多數成為人地奴隸或被人利用! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1cd80ce677168b88c088e126aacd2d7d58e080","tid":186123,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/6e/ac/41/6eac418dfcb123876d9c9163634e70b2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F6e%2Fac%2F41%2F6eac418dfcb123876d9c9163634e70b2.gif&h=43ad24c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6e45be7136c04dd5f2cd211d10cd16efe7c611f","tid":186123,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"p仔留明支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edf01e42c806eb8a95607f6c87f8e2ace09d828","tid":186123,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望巴打團結到 IT 人一齊做啲野出黎"},{"pid":"35ff6f157efd30e4d33041a2ed0def51d925bf8d","tid":186123,"uid":59837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:06:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有個idea, 但唔識寫program ⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7530f7f143e0ad9ce4308a838eab47c42160c1c7","tid":186123,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推呀"},{"pid":"f156159a1e17f0a6084f5dfea77e414617e8eb00","tid":186123,"uid":96741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解呢行會俾人當狗, 就係有你呢D想要成果又唔肯比錢用所謂創業黎昆鳩人既仆街老細. 人工比唔起就算, 而家想免費拎橋, 食屎啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Start Up: Programmer Needed!<br />\nHello, me and my friends are working on a start up and we are looking for a programmer to help us with developing the website. There's no compensation. However, this will be a very valuable experience to add to your resume as well as learning how to do a start up. You can work from scratch or continue to build upon what we already have. If you're interested, please contact me via fb. Thank you.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n外國一樣有。"},{"pid":"e55518ce33458e22cddb5b79993a56e8785d2861","tid":186123,"uid":96741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去d創業活動同d BBA佬夾，個個都係吹水王<br />\n即使個idea係你出又點<br />\n擺明你識寫code你永遠只配做佢手下<br />\n一幅高高在上的樣子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing 不好因為這類經歷失去對人的信任。<br />\n<br />\n要有好的表達技巧，加上好的硬技術，再好好的發現機會，你會發現世界不一樣頭兩項都可以自己努力，但第三項，我真的知道可能點做。<br />\n<br />\n在矽谷無時無刻都有新idea ，但所有人只在乎做得到的，而不是說的漂亮的。無能力想分一份成果的，請出價買作品/股份，而不是&quot;合作&quot;。"},{"pid":"994bd264747e64f5ea53a491d26d7b90a691424d","tid":186123,"uid":96741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望巴打團結到 IT 人一齊做啲野出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果不是想賺錢，有無想過開一個公開的github, 之後在lihkg直接討論?<br />\n為什麼要telegram ?"},{"pid":"1b9e98c01421703222e31c5f00e0ce7ee0a6836f","tid":186123,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"Step 1: 有冇IT人想創業? 我有個絕世idea for APP<br />\nStep 2: 分工我打通人際R生意, 你負責晒個APP<br />\nStep 3: IDEA係咩? 唔會係到講, 真係有興趣先telegram我<br />\nStep 4: 風險? 一係AA, 一係你免費幫我做左先, 搵到錢再AA一半俾你<br />\nStep 5: 做唔到? 實係你廢, 我個idea咁好, 外國都有xxx咁多例子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我都大把idea啦, 全港用電話app傳送個人返工, 全天候無漏洞ATM app, 全港最平最齊貨品search app (根據用戶所在地, 未來一星期天氣及你媽媽心情, 即時update價格within 0.001s)...etc<br />\n<br />\nstartup idea根本係一個好簡單既idea, 一句兩句講完<br />\n好似google咁大間公司, startup idea就係做個好快既search engine<br />\n重點係implementation個陣既idea, 例如google點令engine做到好快<br />\n呢d IT 創業成鳩日硬係有d不知所謂行外既, 話自己idea好<br />\n大佬你連implementation點做都唔識, 你點貢獻阿? 又埋係要IT人諗<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係start idea咁好, 自己既專業又用得上既<br />\n咁你準備份proposal, 去搵投資者, 跟手自己請人啦<br />\n如果你又冇信心, 又冇專業, 又冇資金, 又冇準備, 你又憑乜野要水人落坑? <br />\n#你老母我那有才能.jpg  #最慘仲要覺得自己有貢獻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解我咁憎呢d post? 因為好多時出呢類post既人<br />\n一係冇專業, 一係冇準備, 一係冇決心, 仲要冇腦到覺得說服到人<br />\n好心有心既就自己諗清楚先啦, 決定好晒先正式搵人合作創業, 咪再黎搵人笨啦"},{"pid":"b03d65355528d89c999a31fe69b53169cc838a21","tid":186123,"uid":96741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Step 1: 有冇IT人想創業? 我有個絕世idea for APP<br />\nStep 2: 分工我打通人際R生意, 你負責晒個APP<br />\nStep 3: IDEA係咩? 唔會係到講, 真係有興趣先telegram我<br />\nStep 4: 風險? 一係AA, 一係你免費幫我做左先, 搵到錢再AA一半俾你<br />\nStep 5: 做唔到? 實係你廢, 我個idea咁好, 外國都有xxx咁多例子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我都大把idea啦, 全港用電話app傳送個人返工, 全天候無漏洞ATM app, 全港最平最齊貨品search app (根據用戶所在地, 未來一星期天氣及你媽媽心情, 即時update價格within 0.001s)...etc<br />\n<br />\nstartup idea根本係一個好簡單既idea, 一句兩句講完<br />\n好似google咁大間公司, startup idea就係做個好快既search engine<br />\n重點係implementation個陣既idea, 例如google點令engine做到好快<br />\n呢d IT 創業成鳩日硬係有d不知所謂行外既, 話自己idea好<br />\n大佬你連implementation點做都唔識, 你點貢獻阿? 又埋係要IT人諗<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係start idea咁好, 自己既專業又用得上既<br />\n咁你準備份proposal, 去搵投資者, 跟手自己請人啦<br />\n如果你又冇信心, 又冇專業, 又冇資金, 又冇準備, 你又憑乜野要水人落坑? <br />\n#你老母我那有才能.jpg  #最慘仲要覺得自己有貢獻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解我咁憎呢d post? 因為好多時出呢類post既人<br />\n一係冇專業, 一係冇準備, 一係冇決心, 仲要冇腦到覺得說服到人<br />\n好心有心既就自己諗清楚先啦, 決定好晒先正式搵人合作創業, 咪再黎搵人笨啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經典例子: 時光機好早有人想到，但到這一刻仲未有人實現到。"},{"pid":"b90daa8105c64c5c91b07621266b930e5520b18d","tid":186123,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"我都知現實上好多人想搵 IT 人笨，所以不如有技術既 IT 人出黎創業，依個係原意<br />\n<br />\n想出 idea 而冇技術既，將會被踢出 group<br />\n想入黎請人，都將會被踢出 group"},{"pid":"e6f0211c60c66a17f02d5e7cc2a18bec9593245e","tid":186123,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推呀"},{"pid":"3eac83a3a00ab9a801c614c8d2b93a42835d74c9","tid":186123,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都知現實上好多人想搵 IT 人笨，所以不如有技術既 IT 人出黎創業，依個係原意<br />\n<br />\n想出 idea 而冇技術既，將會被踢出 group<br />\n想入黎請人，都將會被踢出 group</blockquote><br />\n有技術有idea 又點解要share 俾你知？"},{"pid":"439e18d9b45f9a8b01d44e8879fe23fc9b6d36ae","tid":186123,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5710d4dba33c5c3e2d18eb6bfbe1eefbbd2d440","tid":186123,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"啲startup weekly已經夠廢<br />\n估唔倒有人會想搞tg交流呢啲更加廢既嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7baab4d75260a103b02705503ab81e8466842ab","tid":186123,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  推"},{"pid":"12d403595dd93880928a42f4d3cf9c3b715d9129","tid":186123,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<br />\n開group 有撚用咩"},{"pid":"6fb04993a710b698495a7555c3ff4c54f3838da9","tid":186123,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"係人都知香港IT內憂外患乜都齊晒, 個景只有越做越差, 樓主仲叫人創業, 推人去死? 乜L嘢居心先?!"},{"pid":"493ffe2a0afcaf9f043bb3af5f955539feb4eef0","tid":186123,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:19:58.000Z","msg":"又來天仙局<br />\n自己天馬行空<br />\n但又冇料做到<br />\n又冇錢<br />\n就叫人同你所謂合作<br />\n到做到出來就會比你踢開"},{"pid":"35e7072dcc4375c8729598bcf3041e8929b17923","tid":186123,"uid":54177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:23:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都知現實上好多人想搵 IT 人笨，所以不如有技術既 IT 人出黎創業，依個係原意<br />\n<br />\n想出 idea 而冇技術既，將會被踢出 group<br />\n想入黎請人，都將會被踢出 group</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你咩 想揾份pt做都唔撚得<br />\n免費出idea project把撚呀?<br />\nquit算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"