] 點解咁多busi學生想搞IT startup但自己又唔學寫code<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/102825/page/6?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/102825/page/6?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n又係你呀陳生<br />\n周街都係你e種人<br />\n寫個quick sort黎睇睇先決定幫唔幫你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即刻幫陳生整咗個, 陳生唔L駛驚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/233549_9632b63fcf25211ac111b3fb154623cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F233549_9632b63fcf25211ac111b3fb154623cb.jpg&h=9918d3ee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95680b32592ff5e1d0e08fc847a2526e4411b87","tid":186123,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[讀CS] 點解咁多busi學生想搞IT startup但自己又唔學寫code<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/102825/page/6?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/102825/page/6?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n又係你呀陳生<br />\n周街都係你e種人<br />\n寫個quick sort黎睇睇先決定幫唔幫你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即刻幫陳生整咗個, 陳生唔L駛驚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/233549_9632b63fcf25211ac111b3fb154623cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F233549_9632b63fcf25211ac111b3fb154623cb.jpg&h=9918d3ee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面個<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">Haskell quick sort program</span></ins>其實<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係true</span> quick sort嚟, 因為佢只係做咗divide-and-conquer operation, 冇做到in-place operation! 咁攪法個time complexity好似係O(n), worst-case being O(n^2). Performance冇optimized到! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc7aa11269d8e437acbe93f3d6101f5649ccd87","tid":186123,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"跟住呢個 <ins><span style=\"color: green;\">C quick sort program</span></ins> 先係<span style=\"color: green;\">true</span> quick sort, 因為both divide-and-conquer and in-place operations are involved. 個time complexity好似係O(log n), worst-case being O(nlog n). Performance有optimized到! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/204358_b18fd8612a208d00ba5bc7081117f280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F204358_b18fd8612a208d00ba5bc7081117f280.jpg&h=30591991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/204428_6a122a033ac87dc431e2a391fb7291ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F204428_6a122a033ac87dc431e2a391fb7291ed.jpg&h=8422b9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/204511_a7208b6b87786b0998d36ec13aefff55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F204511_a7208b6b87786b0998d36ec13aefff55.jpg&h=1fefb87c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource code is here: <a href=\"https://paste.ofcode.org/79D5qfpvx5cNDhjuQcJ9h3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaste.ofcode.org%2F79D5qfpvx5cNDhjuQcJ9h3&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d4d44cc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://paste.ofcode.org/79D5qfpvx5cNDhjuQcJ9h3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab886ce89ba467c55f6f53c274da582169d5a09","tid":186123,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:19:49.000Z","msg":"BTW, 唔好問我點解唔整埋個true quick sort Haskell program出嚟. 唉, 因為太complex, 見過stackflow有人post過出嚟, 我連睇都未睇得明!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ce6c122ae53f602ab1f72d2656bc31437b8eb0","tid":186123,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BTW, 唔好問我點解唔整埋個true quick sort Haskell program出嚟. 唉, 因為太complex, 見過stackoverflow有人post過出嚟, 我連睇都未睇得明!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5c07e6b15442660ed2aa46ff4dd4b5f06e825556","tid":186123,"uid":102981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無視俾人騎劫左, 繼續推"},{"pid":"bd967360c1dcbe1d3359f0df73ec51cf8d20bdbf","tid":186123,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BTW, 唔好問我點解唔整埋個true quick sort Haskell program出嚟. 唉, 因為太complex, 見過stackflow有人post過出嚟, 我連睇都未睇得明!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識玩一定寫brainfuck"},{"pid":"ba965069e33a00918cf5d68edbdd7584499f0536","tid":186123,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>BTW, 唔好問我點解唔整埋個true quick sort Haskell program出嚟. 唉, 因為太complex, 見過stackflow有人post過出嚟, 我連睇都未睇得明!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識玩一定寫brainfuck</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBF都係Turing complete, 當然可以&quot;玩&quot;到, 但我唔曉, 亦唔想曉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9174176ecdc9d98f14b99f7cff8a47dccfb7fcc3","tid":186123,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟住呢個 <ins><span style=\"color: green;\">C quick sort program</span></ins> 先係<span style=\"color: green;\">true</span> quick sort, 因為both divide-and-conquer and in-place operations are involved. <span style=\"color: red;\">個time complexity好似係O(log n), worst-case being O(nlog n)</span>. Performance有optimized到! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncomparison based sorting嘅lower bound係&Omega;(n log n). 無靠比較嘅sorting algorithm可以快過&Omega;(n log n)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cs.cmu.edu/~avrim/451f11/lectures/lect0913.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cs.cmu.edu%2F~avrim%2F451f11%2Flectures%2Flect0913.pdf&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5f3a4b3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cs.cmu.edu/~avrim/451f11/lectures/lect0913.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nQuick sort嘅worst case time complexity係O(n^2). 如果input係random，可以做到平均O(n log n).  C嘅 quick library有做功夫去令到sorting夠random。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QvgYAQzg1z8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQvgYAQzg1z8&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e9729876\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QvgYAQzg1z8</a>"},{"pid":"2a1ad1364ffc96263de8c1a570126fddd9c7ad1e","tid":186123,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BTW, 唔好問我點解唔整埋個true quick sort Haskell program出嚟. 唉, 因為太complex, 見過stackflow有人post過出嚟, 我連睇都未睇得明!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等我試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0ebfe207fe77d08024f0c6d3083f92342f0de5","tid":186123,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[讀CS] 點解咁多busi學生想搞IT startup但自己又唔學寫code<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/102825/page/6?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/102825/page/6?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n又係你呀陳生<br />\n周街都係你e種人<br />\n寫個quick sort黎睇睇先決定幫唔幫你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即刻幫陳生整咗個, 陳生唔L駛驚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/233549_9632b63fcf25211ac111b3fb154623cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F233549_9632b63fcf25211ac111b3fb154623cb.jpg&h=9918d3ee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面個<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">Haskell quick sort program</span></ins>其實<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係true</span> quick sort嚟, 因為佢只係做咗divide-and-conquer operation, 冇做到in-place operation! <span style=\"color: red;\">咁攪法個time complexity好似係O(n)</span>, worst-case being O(n^2). Performance冇optimized到! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係錯,sorry。如果上面係O(n).我可以用一個list of pointer做sorting先，sort完pointer後用sorted pointer做array operation，咁我就可以做到一個 O(n)嘅array sorting。但information theory話comparison based sorting嘅lower bound係&Omega;(n log n)."},{"pid":"387bcbf7c1268f35f54422bd04dcabf8a1d69d0d","tid":186123,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>BTW, 唔好問我點解唔整埋個true quick sort Haskell program出嚟. 唉, 因為太complex, 見過stackflow有人post過出嚟, 我連睇都未睇得明!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識玩一定寫brainfuck</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBF都係Turing complete, 當然可以&quot;玩&quot;到, 但我唔曉, 亦唔想曉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYou can write a C to BF compiler first <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c081a1a2f8886ac7e0ec54dddd9fdd0055f455a","tid":186123,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跟住呢個 <ins><span style=\"color: green;\">C quick sort program</span></ins> 先係<span style=\"color: green;\">true</span> quick sort, 因為both divide-and-conquer and in-place operations are involved. <span style=\"color: red;\">個time complexity好似係O(log n), worst-case being O(nlog n)</span>. Performance有optimized到! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncomparison based sorting嘅lower bound係&Omega;(n log n). 無靠比較嘅sorting algorithm可以快過&Omega;(n log n)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cs.cmu.edu/~avrim/451f11/lectures/lect0913.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cs.cmu.edu%2F~avrim%2F451f11%2Flectures%2Flect0913.pdf&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5f3a4b3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cs.cmu.edu/~avrim/451f11/lectures/lect0913.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nQuick sort嘅worst case time complexity係O(n^2). 如果input係random，可以做到平均O(n log n).  C嘅 quick library有做功夫去令到sorting夠random。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QvgYAQzg1z8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQvgYAQzg1z8&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e9729876\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QvgYAQzg1z8</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哈哈, C4F兄做乜騎劫我騎劫人地嘅post! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}